#### Day 19: State-Driven AI Workflows & Psychometric Profiling
* **Objective:** Move beyond single-shot AI prompts by engineering a state-driven, multi-stage interactive pipeline. The goal was to build an AI agent that dynamically adjusts its complexity based on initial user inputs, conducts predictive analytics, and synthesizes behavioral data into a final output artifact.
